OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBritain must train citizen 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Farmy, military chief warns 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Britain should train a "citizen army"  
OL,6, ready to fight a war on land in the    
OL,7, future, the head of the Army has said. 
OL,9,FGeneral Sir Patrick Sanders warned that
OL,10,Fan increase in reserve forces alone    
OL,11,F"would not be enough".                 
OL,13,FHe highlighted the threat from Russia  
OL,14,Fand pointed to steps being taken by    
OL,15,Fother European nations to put their    
OL,16,Fpopulations on a "war footing".        
OL,18,FHe also called for more to be done to  
OL,19,Fequip and modernise the UK's armed     
OL,20,Fforces.                                
